title: Neil Young's gift to Greenland: Free access to his entire music catalog
description: Neil Young is offering free access to his entire music catalog to residents of Greenland. He announced this on his blog on Tuesday in a bid to ease stress amid tensions involving the U.S. and NATO.

description: NATO Secretary-General Mark Rutte warned European leaders they cannot defend themselves without U.S. support, saying Europe would need 10% GDP spending on defense.

title: Neil Young gives Greenland his music for free over Trump 'stress'
description: Neil Young offered Greenland free access to his music due to the "unwarranted stress and threats you are experiencing" from President Donald Trump.
